Alfredo Sauce
https://www.facebook.com/buzzfeedtasty/videos/2726094934309805/?v=2726094934309805

8 tbsp Butter
1 clove Garlic
Salt & Pepper
1 cup Heavy Cream
1 1/2 cup Parmesan Cheese
Parsley

Bring butter to a simmer over medium heat
Add garlic, a pinch of salt and pepper
Stir
Add heavy cream
Stir & Bring to a simmer
Add Parmesan cheese & Parsley
Stir